General Information

PAW DigestiCare 60 is a multi-strain, multi-species probiotic and wholefood powder for the maintenance of everyday digestive health of dogs, cats and other companion animals.

Common Uses

Provide good bacteria to restore and improve intestinal balance. Aid during period of intestinal dysfunction, including treatment and control of diarrhoea. Exclude and suppress bad bacteria such as E.coli and Salmonella. Aid in the establishment of gastrointestinal microflora of physiologically immature animals (puppies & kittens). Deliver essential amino and fatty acids, key vitamins and minerals. Suitable for dogs, cats and other companion animal. Each 2 grams dose contains 60 Million CFU of 'good bacteria'. Highly palatable powder that can easily be sprinkled onto your pet's food. Includes a 4 g measuring scoop for an easy usage.

Ingredients

7 strain probiotic powder at 60,000,000 cfu / 2 g (Lactobacillus acidophilus; L.delbrueckii subspecies bulgaricus; L.lantarum; L. rhamnosus; Bifidobacterium bifidum; Enterococcus faecium;Streptococcus alivarius. Naturally fermented organic whole grains and seeds, alfalfa grass, quinoa, spirulina and other legumes and cereals to provide easily absorbed nutritional support.subspecies thermophilus)
